{"tid":368572,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"布吉4日3夜,求屌 有d長","createTime":"2017-08-21T15:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T10:41:26.000Z","uid":126894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a17405955a4663e77996888867dddd78b06c3598","tid":368572,"uid":126894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:37:51.000Z","msg":"Day one :<br />\n凌晨機到,先住機場附近酒店.<br />\n<br />\nDay Two<br />\n唱錢,之後去番機場搭van 去check in 酒店, book 左patong beach 附近一間<br />\n之後去玩  Flying Hanuman (邊到book 最平)應該想簡journey B<br />\n之後去番酒吧街食野,行夜市等等 <br />\n去no 6 餐廳食野(有無其他介紹)<br />\n順便去到jungceylon 附近報埋tour (係咪當地報平d,有無話大約幾錢) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay three<br />\n浮潛(諗緊斯米蘭定皇帝島) <br />\n玩完都係去下Patong area 食野行beach food<br />\n去big c Supermarket<br />\nbanzaan fresh market 食海鮮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay three<br />\nAtv(諗緊玩唔玩,好似好恐怖咁,仲有無咩活動提議)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩完就直接由patong 去cape panwa (係咪得taxi 簡,車費大約幾多)<br />\nBook 左間酒店係cape panwa附近<br />\nday 3 / 4 諗住relax 多d 去做下spa 同享用下酒店設施.<br />\n有無邊間Spa 好推介,暫時睇到有間叫shine spa 好似幾好<br />\n<br />\nDay4<br />\nCheckout 酒店<br />\n之後去做spa (有無邊間Spa 好推介,暫時睇到有間叫shine spa 好似幾好) <br />\n之後5:30 去sri panwa 個baba nest 到玩<br />\n食Dinner (諗住出番patong 食/cape panwa 有咩推介)(驚cape panwa 無車去機場)<br />\n食完9點幾,仲有無咩spa / 按摩可做. 因為凌晨3:40am 先飛機,有無話最遲幾點去機場(唔想太夜捱咁貴車費去機場)<br />\n<br />\nday 5<br />\n機場等到3:40am 飛機返hk<br />\n<br />\n求屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nzipliner 去到當地報會唔會平d 定即日報可能無位?<br />\n當地d tour 大約咩價位.... <br />\n唱錢係咪去間叫airport exchange 到唱or superich<br />\n由patong 去cape panwa (係咪得taxi 簡,車費大約幾多)"},{"pid":"cf846bc05df1069a4583ebb6368a98889b04e733","tid":368572,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"你係女既話大把人掙住屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bc175a9b2d8be8063de87d40411681f43f82f2","tid":368572,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係女既話大把人掙住屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70af1a0ec1fbce59a8cf8777e65fbc5af8df4817","tid":368572,"uid":126894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/002626_03905ca3ac95b99ae157f533dc2f6417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F002626_03905ca3ac95b99ae157f533dc2f6417.jpg&h=4b3275bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/002627_03905ca3ac95b99ae157f533dc2f6417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F002627_03905ca3ac95b99ae157f533dc2f6417.jpg&h=a325e51e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/002627_3043bda814254087a220f96119642990.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F002627_3043bda814254087a220f96119642990.jpg&h=ed8b1837&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24411b438c0ceea4e6c8d2d5087af71add97dd09","tid":368572,"uid":126894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:17:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35122f25d28362ebb187f7481e2e9bf4a49c3054","tid":368572,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:33:33.000Z","msg":"推 就黎去布吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80056dc587f060d3944a9aa1d80cdeae5cf41eda","tid":368572,"uid":126894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T06:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推 就黎去布吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩行程share 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0f5101a3707861f4786cca0a5771736f0f04a2","tid":368572,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:21:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>推 就黎去布吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩行程share 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇時間你應該係搭hk express?<br />\n我地都係類似喳<br />\n頭兩日巴東 spa 食海鮮 飛索 酒吧街<br />\n第三日住泳池villa<br />\n第四日跟local tour去皇帝島<br />\n第五日應該9hea 行下超市 又做多次spa 食晚餐慢慢去機場"},{"pid":"ed0c2cefbeb5af260fb9b7c3c6ef6621e9bf2f7c","tid":368572,"uid":16469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Day one :<br />\n凌晨機到,先住機場附近酒店.<br />\n<br />\nDay Two<br />\n唱錢,之後去番機場搭van 去check in 酒店, book 左patong beach 附近一間<br />\n之後去玩  Flying Hanuman (邊到book 最平)應該想簡journey B<br />\n之後去番酒吧街食野,行夜市等等 <br />\n去no 6 餐廳食野(有無其他介紹)<br />\n順便去到jungceylon 附近報埋tour (係咪當地報平d,有無話大約幾錢) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay three<br />\n浮潛(諗緊斯米蘭定皇帝島) <br />\n玩完都係去下Patong area 食野行beach food<br />\n去big c Supermarket<br />\nbanzaan fresh market 食海鮮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay three<br />\nAtv(諗緊玩唔玩,好似好恐怖咁,仲有無咩活動提議)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩完就直接由patong 去cape panwa (係咪得taxi 簡,車費大約幾多)<br />\nBook 左間酒店係cape panwa附近<br />\nday 3 / 4 諗住relax 多d 去做下spa 同享用下酒店設施.<br />\n有無邊間Spa 好推介,暫時睇到有間叫shine spa 好似幾好<br />\n<br />\nDay4<br />\nCheckout 酒店<br />\n之後去做spa (有無邊間Spa 好推介,暫時睇到有間叫shine spa 好似幾好) <br />\n之後5:30 去sri panwa 個baba nest 到玩<br />\n食Dinner (諗住出番patong 食/cape panwa 有咩推介)(驚cape panwa 無車去機場)<br />\n食完9點幾,仲有無咩spa / 按摩可做. 因為凌晨3:40am 先飛機,有無話最遲幾點去機場(唔想太夜捱咁貴車費去機場)<br />\n<br />\nday 5<br />\n機場等到3:40am 飛機返hk<br />\n<br />\n求屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nzipliner 去到當地報會唔會平d 定即日報可能無位?<br />\n當地d tour 大約咩價位.... <br />\n唱錢係咪去間叫airport exchange 到唱or superich<br />\n由patong 去cape panwa (係咪得taxi 簡,車費大約幾多)</blockquote><br />\n之前都係夜機去夜機返 三日三夜<br />\n浮潛去左去左斯米蘭 啲水好清 好正 但車程同船程加埋來回太耐 四五個鐘 建議你去皇帝島<br />\nATV一定要玩 好刺激 係男仔都實中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBook tour 我個陣同bj@1998th@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n報 直接email 同佢講幾點想玩乜就得 佢會覆你有咩plan"},{"pid":"702a9b16478e210278a349de4ee0b80c02b8b21a","tid":368572,"uid":126894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推 就黎去布吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩行程share 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇時間你應該係搭hk express?<br />\n我地都係類似喳<br />\n頭兩日巴東 spa 食海鮮 飛索 酒吧街<br />\n第三日住泳池villa<br />\n第四日跟local tour去皇帝島<br />\n第五日應該9hea 行下超市 又做多次spa 食晚餐慢慢去機場</blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n而家係睇d tour 上網報定去到先報 唔知價錢差幾遠呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"851f2d53c204b6aad9cc6a461aabdf5a4974337c","tid":368572,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推 就黎去布吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩行程share 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇時間你應該係搭hk express?<br />\n我地都係類似喳<br />\n頭兩日巴東 spa 食海鮮 飛索 酒吧街<br />\n第三日住泳池villa<br />\n第四日跟local tour去皇帝島<br />\n第五日應該9hea 行下超市 又做多次spa 食晚餐慢慢去機場</blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n而家係睇d tour 上網報定去到先報 唔知價錢差幾遠呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我朋友話去到會平啲<br />\n所以我唔搵啦信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題係 巴東搵tour係方便<br />\n但我地去tour果陣係住山卡啦villa<br />\n所以預埋要接送費<br />\n<br />\n聽聞可以試下講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你幾多號去？"},{"pid":"7d27e7de040e3b9e9a2e4c3aef011358cdbda60a","tid":368572,"uid":126894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T11:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推 就黎去布吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩行程share 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇時間你應該係搭hk express?<br />\n我地都係類似喳<br />\n頭兩日巴東 spa 食海鮮 飛索 酒吧街<br />\n第三日住泳池villa<br />\n第四日跟local tour去皇帝島<br />\n第五日應該9hea 行下超市 又做多次spa 食晚餐慢慢去機場</blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n而家係睇d tour 上網報定去到先報 唔知價錢差幾遠呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我朋友話去到會平啲<br />\n所以我唔搵啦信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題係 巴東搵tour係方便<br />\n但我地去tour果陣係住山卡啦villa<br />\n所以預埋要接送費<br />\n<br />\n聽聞可以試下講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你幾多號去？</blockquote><br />\n11月去 <br />\n所以我頭2日玩tour 都係住近patong 之後最尾去到山卡啦歎酒店做spa<br />\ntour 應該都係當地報（我想知大約咩價位，到時可以跟住黎講價）， 但zipline 去到當地報都應該無得平？ 同埋我怕即日報無晒位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇你幾山卡啦 我見panwa 呢d 都會去車埋 ,可能加你1-200 上網睇過係 , 唔太肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5bbcf170900f8abe8e639a67196b94ea6b25bc","tid":368572,"uid":80369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"布吉主要係搭&quot;TUKTUK&quot;<br />\nTAXI都有  不過少見D<br />\n<br />\nTOUR去到先報會平D<br />\n一開始殺佢一半都唔過份<br />\n反正佢都會還價<br />\n<br />\n記得問埋由酒店去到玩既地方要坐幾耐車<br />\n上次去玩激流要坐個半鐘車<br />\n個鬼佬團友未去到已經嘔緊<br />\n<br />\n飛索其實一般  頭一兩次就覺得刺激<br />\n全日都飛就開始悶<br />\n同埋有心理準備D TOUR包既午餐都係好難食<br />\n<br />\nATV都正既  但玩完會全身都係泥<br />\n如果你鍾意揸車可以玩埋高卡車<br />\n<br />\n出島/浮潛就唔好去PP島喇 俾大陸人攻陷左<br />\n<br />\n仲有反轉屋,老虎園個D可以去影相 不過全部都俾錢"},{"pid":"b76f227222046b87a8026126bea340dd9e72d7ef","tid":368572,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推 就黎去布吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有咩行程share 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇時間你應該係搭hk express?<br />\n我地都係類似喳<br />\n頭兩日巴東 spa 食海鮮 飛索 酒吧街<br />\n第三日住泳池villa<br />\n第四日跟local tour去皇帝島<br />\n第五日應該9hea 行下超市 又做多次spa 食晚餐慢慢去機場</blockquote><br />\n係呀<br />\n而家係睇d tour 上網報定去到先報 唔知價錢差幾遠呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我朋友話去到會平啲<br />\n所以我唔搵啦信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但問題係 巴東搵tour係方便<br />\n但我地去tour果陣係住山卡啦villa<br />\n所以預埋要接送費<br />\n<br />\n聽聞可以試下講價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你幾多號去？<