pps Grab <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJungceylon 近m字酒店 方向 有間好多咬腳魚嘅店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講下講下佢又肯<br />\nZipline因為間間差唔多 價錢又叫唔到太多 又反正包接送咪聽佢推介果間 都唔錯有相送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad9a59b59887f36b89bbf1931cbb9ce731ce104","tid":368572,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"唱錢我係香港唱 我啲朋友搵機禁 要收150b手續費<br />\nCall車就 我都唔知呀哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚試用強國apps訂車去機場 86蚊人仔 睇下點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5416de8433d548c328390fd5f1e37b4a242e3307","tid":368572,"uid":138706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T00:35:10.000Z","msg":"報local tour可以去到當地先報，周街都有，是但塭間都一定平過你係香港塭agent報，，我自己就係街邊覺得個姐姐望落nice 覺得價錢接受到就一次過報哂幾日行程啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> flying human係公價黎，間間報同價，好玩，建議玩最貴個plan，因為果個先有包玩入面飛最長兩分鐘個條，真心正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外激流都唔錯 好好玩，不過都係睇人，甘岩帶我船個好識搞氣氛，其實刺唔刺激係佢地做出黎 好多下都係佢故意撞到反"},{"pid":"d0977415ca31077a394728aa02d09da4a3db81a0","tid":368572,"uid":126894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唱錢我係香港唱 我啲朋友搵機禁 要收150b手續費<br />\nCall車就 我都唔知呀哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今晚試用強國apps訂車去機場 86蚊人仔 睇下點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解珊瑚島唔推介既 , 我都plan 係皇帝+珊瑚 聽完好似就咁去皇帝就夠 都係主要浮潛<img src=\"/assets/face